      "content": "thanks. i tried some juice but i still feel kinda weird and my vision is getting a bit blurry. i was thinking maybe my sugar is actually spiking because of the stress of the run and that's why the juice didn't work right away. if i take a small corrective dose of insulin now just to be safe, would that help stabilize me?",
